**Lawyer** | Mafia Power 
__Basics__
The **lawyer** may choose one player each night to apply a *basic disguise* to. The player is disguised as an in-play town role. The **lawyer** may not disguise the same person on consecutive nights.

__Formalized__
Inherit: `Mafia Attack`
Starting: Join #Mafia
Pre-End Night: Weakly Disguise @Selection as @(AliveOnly:False,OrigAlign:Townsfolk)->RandomPlayer->OriginalRole (~NextDay) [Quantity: %Number%, Succession: No Target Succession] |lawyer.1|
